Key Match Events: Subhi Al Dawi skillfully dribbled past the Amavubi defenders before scoring in the 15th minute.
Nshuti Innocent equalized for Amavubi in the 62nd minute with a well-executed goal.
Fiacre Ntwari made a crucial save to deny Ahmed Ekrawa’s close-range attempt in the second half.
Post-Match Reflections: Amavubi’s next challenge will be against Nigeria, a match that could prove pivotal in their journey to Morocco in 2025.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match took place at Tripoli Stadium on Wednesday, September 4, 2024.
